    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Lights, electronic apparatus, or other devices that emit identifying signals related to their position to guide or warn navigators or pilots of aircraft or ships.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000027751/McGraw-Hill Dictionary of Scientific and Technical Terms (1978)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Luces, aparatos electrónicos u otros elementos que emiten señales de identificación relacionados con su posición para guiar o alertar a navegantes o pilotos de aviones o barcos.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Lichten, elektronische apparaten of andere middelen die herkenbare signalen uitzenden die te maken hebben met hun ligging. Ze begeleiden of waarschuwen zeevaarders of piloten van vliegtuigen of schepen.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
